Effects
Damage over time.
Bleed -- Take damage at the start of your turn for each stack.  If it does not get reapplied after a turn, you no longer bleed.
Poison -- Take damage equal to stacks.  Lose one stack.
Burn -- Take damage equal to stacks.

Disarm -- One less action point per stack of disarm.
Cripple -- One less movement point per stack.  (Can still move through abilities)
Immobilized -- Can't move this turn.